name: Hide the Pain Harold The Movie

metadata.name: Hide the Pain Harold #1
metadata.description: Hide the Pain Harold is a collection of 10 unique meme NFTs celebrating the project of “Hide the Pain Harold: The Movie.” Each NFT is a real storyboard picture from the pre-production of the “Hide the Pain Harold: The Movie”, featuring the legendary meme star András Arató (Hide the Pain Harold). The NFT collectibles live on Ethereum blockchain, and the rare NFT holders will have the opportunity to appear in a cameo role in the Hide the Pain Harold movie.
